high_descs: Walk on and take your left near the dresser.
Turn on your cellphone and reach the cupboard front.
Take the mobile phone on the safe near the ac remote.
Put the cellphone into the safe near the cupboard.
Turn around your right and find another one mobile phone on another shelf opposite to bed.
Take the cellphone on the lower shelf opposite to the bed.
Turn left and walk on to the safe.
Put the cellphone on the safe.
anns.task_desc: Collect the CellPhones and put on the Safe.

high_descs: Head straight and turn left near the dresser.
Pick up the cellphone from the table.
Turn right and head straight, then hang right and then again turn back towards the safe.
Put the cellphone inside the safe.
Turn around and turn left towards the shelf.
Pick up the cellphone from the table.
Turn left and head straight towards the safe.
Put the cellphone inside the safe.
anns.task_desc: Collecting CellPhone from different locations in the room and placing them on the bottom of the Safe.

high_descs: Head to the dresser in the front.
Pick up the cellphone from the dresser.
Head to the safe on the right.
Put the cellphone in the safe.
Turn around to reach the shelf.
Pick up the cellphone from the bottom shelf.
Turn left to reach the safe.
Put the cellphone in the safe.
anns.task_desc: Put two CellPhones in the Safe.
